“DIFFERENT TIMES” 

June 22 6-10pm 
28 Rue du Petit Musc 75004

A photo exhibition by Lukas Gansterer x Li-Ning chronicling 3 years of travel through LA/NY/Paris/Florence/Miami/Copenhagen. 

🇫🇷 @lining.official x @dark_white @zach.allen_ @daveysayles @sontinga

Whirlwind of a week in Paris❤️‍🔥✨
Thank you to everyone for coming out to the show. 

Li-Ning and Erik Ellington present "Different Times", an exhibition shot by Lukas Gansterer between 2021 and 2023 while traveling through New York City, Miami, Los Angeles, Paris, Copenhagen, and Florence.
Featuring Erik Ellington, Zach Allen, Davey Sayles, and Tinga Johnson.

Thank you to the team at @lining.official and our friends in Paris for joining for the opening. 
All those who contributed to bring it to life, I appreciate you so much, big love ❤️

For the first time, I’m setting up a @humanrecreationalservices exhibition at #ComplexCon this year! 

I’ve hidden 5 keys around Los Angeles. Each key is a pass (day of your choice) for pair of tickets to #ComplexCon.

Tune in tomorrow Tuesday 14th at 11am PST at @humanrecreationalservices for the locations!

See you there and happy hunting.

📸 @giovannireda
